Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.10,0:21:26.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\an9\bord0\shad0\c&H0F1B1F&\fs-4\frz350.1\pos(1142,190)\fade(700,0)}我的奴隶日记
